{"TopicId":195300,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"The Laythe 0 challenge!","CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-03T20:00:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-03T20:00:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe story:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe KSP is in debt because of the crash of the most expensive rocket ever made. To make up for the lost funds, KSP accepted a contract to gather a surface sample from Laythe. But since the KSP is in debt, the mission must not waste any money. Thus the rocket has to be made with 0 funds or less. This seems impossible since fuel cost money and you can\u0027t go anyway without fuel. But impossible is not a thing at \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E. So its up to you to save KSP!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmodes:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#2ecc71;\u0022\u003Eeasy: Do a flyby of Laythe for (or less than) 0 funds.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#f39c12;\u0022\u003Emedium: land on Laythe and get a surface sample, all for 0 funds or less.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003EHard: land on Laythe and get 100 or more science, for 0 funds or less. \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuper: Impress \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E (and me!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRules:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnot allowed:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nDocking and getting fuel and other resources from other ships/bases\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLanding in the sea\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLanding at other planets except Kerbin(you may enter orbit)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nKilling \u003Cstrong\u003Eany \u003C/strong\u003Ekerbal\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nusing cheats (obviously!)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nusing deployed science from the DLC (other parts allowed)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nusing ion engines\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nrestoring science (except from the lab)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nApollo stye (leaving something in orbit while landing a lander)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nFlag: needs some refining:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022The-Laythe-0-challenge.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.00\u0022 height=\u0022720\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/gzjcCjT/The-Laythe-0-challenge.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-07-04T04:31:28Z\u0022 title=\u002207/04/2020 04:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 4, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Cant think of a username\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-03T20:34:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to clarify, for anyone confused, I believe that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204905-cant-think-of-a-username/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204905\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204905-cant-think-of-a-username/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Cant think of a username\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0intends for us to\u00A0 mine for profit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-04T00:08:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, but getting an huge tanker to Laythe is no easy task!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sturmhauke","CreatedById":190611,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-04T02:02:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about getting a contract that results in a net profit?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-04T04:21:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223814520\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195300\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221593828164\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022190611\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sturmhauke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, sturmhauke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about getting a contract that results in a net profit?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is differant\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flying dutchman","CreatedById":189896,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-04T09:28:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni don\u0027t get why apollo style should not be allowed..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xendelaar","CreatedById":139535,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-04T10:47:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsorry if this is a dumb question, but how do I get a ship on the launchpad with zero funds in the bank account?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-05T05:08:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223814719\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195300\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221593859624\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139535\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022xendelaar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, xendelaar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsorry if this is a dumb question, but how do I get a ship on the launchpad with zero funds in the bank account?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nno it is no a dumb question at all. I haven\u0027t thought of that! Just pretend!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-05T05:31:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223814702\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195300\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221593854908\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022189896\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flying dutchman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, Flying dutchman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni don\u0027t get why apollo style should not be allowed..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, I saying that the best way is using an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-07-05T05:33:03Z\u0022 title=\u002207/05/2020 05:33  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 5, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Cant think of a username\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-22T22:15:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223814316\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195300\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221593806456\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204905\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cant think of a username\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/3/2020 at 1:00 PM, Cant think of a username said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRules:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnot allowed:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nDocking and getting fuel and other resources from other ships/bases\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLanding in the sea\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLanding at other planets except Kerbin(you may enter orbit)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nKilling \u003Cstrong\u003Eany \u003C/strong\u003Ekerbal\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nusing cheats (obviously!)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nusing deployed science from the DLC (other parts allowed)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nusing ion engines\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nrestoring science (except from the lab)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nApollo stye (leaving something in orbit while landing a lander)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n7. is pretty much an unnecessary restriction. No one in their right mind would waste xenon in a tanker that\u0027s supposed to generate a surplus unless said tanker is meant to go like 20 km/s.\u00A0Xenon is ~500 times the cost of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Liquid Fuel and Oxidizer\u0022\u003ELFO\u003C/abbr\u003E for 12 times the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Specific Impulse (rocketry) or Internet Service Provider\u0022\u003EISP\u003C/abbr\u003E and can\u0027t be made via \u003Cabbr title=\u0022In-Situ Resource Utilization\u0022\u003EISRU\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdditionally, you may want to make some kind of rule that prevents you from mining/converting and reselling the ore on Kerbin to fund a throwaway mission.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-07-23T01:43:51Z\u0022 title=\u002207/23/2020 01:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Pds314\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cant think of a username","CreatedById":204905,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-23T02:07:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy mission so far:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nlaunch a huge \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003Essto\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ngot into a Laythe orbit\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nexploded upon entry\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ncrashed\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nkilled kerbal (BTW that\u0027s not allowed)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nSecond attempt:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nadded heat shields\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nlanded on laythe\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ndid the stuff\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ntried to liftoff\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nmy craft was too heavy after the ore was loaded\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ncrashed\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ndid not kill kerbals\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThird attempt:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nremade ship\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nlanded on laythe\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nrescued the last kerbals\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\ngot into Laythe orbit.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nrealized that I did not have \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003Edv\u003C/abbr\u003E to go back and have spare fuel to make the mission 0 funds\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\naborted mission and when home anyway\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nFourth attempt:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nremade ship\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nbrought too less fuel\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nwent home\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nFifth attempt:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nin progress.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}